{
  "stem": "24830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For the people, when you were living--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We put them in hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have quite a few family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was the only one to know where they were.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in apartment, in house, in a-- in a monastery, convent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the most interesting place that we find was a leprosy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know leprosy?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It's a terrible sickness.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody will ever go there, especially not the German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had some people there, and in-- in church, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of priest and minister help a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my work--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were in hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And who would do the-- who would do the--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I go and ask them for a picture.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then first, we had a mailbox in somebody's house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But too much-- you know, we went there too often.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was too dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we find a better idea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was a photographer in Nice, [FRENCH], actually.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he had a-- you know, how do you call?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A business right there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then to be safe, he took picture of all of us, because we came and bring the picture, and whatever we want.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then a few days later, we'll come back to pick up the false identity.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So in case-- in case somebody was there, then I say, oh, I come to pick up my picture.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he will have give us, you know, so there was no-- not to worry.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was finally deported.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he didn't come back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So-- Did he actually do the papers too?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The thing is, the paper-- see, what was so dangerous-- anyway, I was lucky.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
